ts commits without a verified proof path.\n    - Define a minimal validation rule set (existence, structure, correspondence); record failure types on each rejection to tune constraint strictness.", :xt/id "00f6da8c-35e1-488e-8c5c-480a96534651"} {:entity/id "00fb0862-cb93-4a83-8361-da2f66cdf3cc", :entity/name "futon5a-d/excursion/networked-intelligence", :entity/type :excursion/doc, :entity/external-id "E-networked-intelligence", :entity/source "excursion-doc-watcher", :entity/props {:excursion/id "networked-intelligence", :excursion/title "Networked Intelligence as Hypergraph of Daily Frames", :excursion/status "unknown", :excursion/parent-mission nil}, :xt/id "00fb0862-cb93-4a83-8361-da2f66cdf3cc"} {:entity/id "010b202d-b4f5-45e9-af9b-9d2eb07e709c", :entity/name "iiching/exotype-225/05-then", :entity/type :pattern/component, :entity/external-id "THEN", :entity/source "program/params until lift mappings land.\n    Use the encoding fields for identification and the futon5 manifest for", :xt/id "010b202d-b4f5-45e9-af9b-9d2eb07e709c"} {:entity/id "010b6f4c-ba6d-485e-9442-5632de711bf6", :entity/name "iiching/exotype-028/context", :entity/type :pattern/clause, :entity/external-id "iiching/exotype-028/context", :entity/source "Canonical 8-bit encoding for exotype 028.", :xt/id "010b6f4c-ba6d-485e-9442-5632de711bf6"} {:entity/id "010cbaa9-cc5c-4f3c-9616-915aad3e54d3", :entity/name "iiching/exotype-167/context", :entity/type :pattern/clause, :entity/external-id "iiching/exotype-167/context", :entity/source "Canonical 8-bit encoding for exotype 167.", :xt/id "010cbaa9-cc5c-4f3c-9616-915aad3e54d3"} {:entity/id "011069dc-bd05-46c2-9691-b29b2ffeb1ca", :entity/name "workflow-coherence/sphere-equilibrium/context", :entity/type :pattern/clause, :entity/external-id "workflow-coherence/sphere-equilibrium/context", :entity/source "Work naturally clusters into five spheres with different rhythms and demands; imbalance in any sphere propagates stress to the others.", :xt/id "011069dc-b